01:59.630 --> 02:02.100
Oh, hey, welcome to my own private beach.

02:04.800 --> 02:07.810
It's, uh... nice,
but it's missing something.

02:08.940 --> 02:10.910
The ocean?

02:10.940 --> 02:13.610
Good point.

02:13.650 --> 02:16.880
Oceans and seas, waves and tides...

02:18.750 --> 02:22.050
Fine. We'll close up the shop
and go to the beach.

